snippet.title: Minecraft x Hello Kitty® and Friends DLC
snippet.description:
Step into the adorable world of Hello Kitty® in this delightful DLC, where farming meets friendship! Create your own cozy farm, grow crops, and raise cute animals alongside beloved Sanrio® characters like Hello Kitty, Cinnamoroll™, Kuromi™, and more. Join in on fun seasonal events like spring egg hunts and fall pumpkin carving! Upgrade your home with over 180 new furniture options for lots of added charm. For a limited time, you can also stop by the Dressing Room for your free Hello Kitty Outfit! Whether you’re planting crops or celebrating with friends, there’s never been a sweeter simulator. 
Read more : https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/marketplace/pdp?id=a9caa9a3-20a8-4a32-b29f-bede435d95cb
